Price OverviewPrice Detail

Price Overview chart shows development of price over time
  • How often is this game on sale? Are deals getting better?
  • How quickly did it reach current historical low?
  • Is historical low being repeated?
  • Is the regular price of the game dropping?
  • Do all stores drop price?
Price Detail chart shows a per-store view of price history
  • When and how good deals did a store have?
  • Do all stores have deals at the same time?
  • How much prices differ between stores?
  • Are there any differences between sale frequency?
\r\n

Cut OverviewSavings

Cut Overview chart shows development of price cuts over time
  • How often is this game on sale? What is the deals cut?
  • How often are deals repeated?
  • How quickly did price cuts reached current level?
Savings chart shows absolute value of price cut
If regular price drops, same price cut won't mean same savings
\r\n

Sales DistributionSales Duration

Sales distribution chart can tell you when there usually is a sale during a year
  • When are deals more frequent?
  • Are deals with higher cut more frequent during certain time of year?
Note that frequency is aggregate over all historical data and all selected stores
Sales duration chart may tell you how long a sale usually lasts
  • Do deals with smaller cut last longer? By how much?
  • What is a median duration of a sale?
  • How many times was a game on sale with a price cut?
Note that frequency is aggregate over all historical data and all selected stores

As ye venture out onto the docks of Melee Island, there'll be a shock to yer system the likes of which you've never seen. The Secret of Monkey Island: Special Edition gives you the world you remember, yet it be shown to ya like only yer imagination could. It seems Guybrush Threepwood, a young lad wantin' to be a bloodthirsty pirate is back to relive his hunt fo the fabled riches of Monkey Island. Hilarious swashbuckling misadventures: Embark on a bumbling misadventure in an attempt to become the most infamous pirate in the Caribbean, win the heart of the beautiful governor, Elaine Marley, and confront the evil ghost pirate, LeChuck! High-definition graphics: The game is all-new and re-imagined with a contemporary art style, hand-drawn and presented in 1080p. Complete voice over using original Monkey Island franchise cast members brings the story and characters to life like never before. Renewed music score: Enjoy the re-mastered and re-recorded musical score using live instruments. Special Edition and Classic modes: Scene-for-scene hot swap lets you seamlessly transition between Special Edition and Classic modes at anytime during gameplay. Enhanced gameplay: The all-new intuitive game interface and controls provide a more interactive gameplay experience. Hint system: Not sure what to do next? The in-game puzzle hint system keeps the puzzles fresh and fun. [LucasArts]
— Metacritic.com
